message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite the repository release and the
  accompanying preprint. https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.29139
title: "How Token Influence Decays with Distance: A Green-Function View of Trained Language Models"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Brändel"
    given-names: "Matthias"
  - family-names: "Köhler"
    given-names: "Stephan"
  - family-names: "Rheinbach"
