version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-07-13"
license: "BSD-3-Clause"
repository-code: "https://github.com/"
url: "https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.29139"
abstract: >-
  Minimal reference implementation for measuring distance-resolved Jacobian
  sensitivities of next-token logits with respect to earlier input-token
  embeddings, together with decay-model fitting and representative Pythia and
  Qwen experiment configurations.
keywords:
  - language models
  - transformers
  - automatic differentiation
  - Jacobian sensitivity
  - Green function
  - power-law decay
  - hierarchical models
